						<summary>

						<p>On a stone lying near the Īśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1544 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1466, Krōdhin, Kārtika śu. 12,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1544 A.D., October 27 (Monday).</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the remission of the barber's tax and other levies such as <hi rend="italic">siddhāyam, kāṇika,</hi> etc. in Gajarāmapalle-agrahāram in Gutti-durgam by Rāyalu Rāmarāju.</p>						

